.SH NAME
\*LXmScaleSetValue\*O\(emA Scale function that sets a slider value
.iX "XmScaleSetValue"
.iX "Scale functions" "XmScaleSetValue"
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sS
.iS
\&#include <Xm/Scale.h>
.sp \n(PDu
void XmScaleSetValue (\*Vwidget, value\*L)
.ta .5i 1.5i
	Widget	\*Vwidget\*L;
	int	\*Vvalue\*L;
.wH .fi
.iE
.sE
.SH DESCRIPTION
\*LXmScaleSetValue\*O sets the slider \*Vvalue\*O within the
Scale widget.
.VL 1i 
.LI "\*Vwidget\*O"
Specifies the Scale widget ID.
.LI "\*Vvalue\*O"
Specifies the slider position along the scale.
This sets the \*LXmNvalue\*O resource.
.LE 
.PP 
